I have always been passionate about using ingenuity and intelligent technology to expand the potential of physicians to heal without constraints and improve patient outcomes through minimally invasive care, and I envision myself contributing my talent to furthering Intuitive Surgical's mission to make surgery smarter, safer, and more human. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

